"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Bad weather is delaying US President Donald Trump's rally, which he called a 'spectacular' celebration. Over 165 million people are facing dangerous heat and humidity, with temperatures expected to remain at 38C (100F) for several days.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump Rally Delayed\",            \"translated_version\": \"El mal clima est\u00e1 retrasando el mitin del presidente de EE.UU. Donald Trump, que llam\u00f3 una celebraci\u00f3n espectacular. M\u00e1s de 165 millones de personas enfrentan calor y humedad peligrosos, con temperaturas que se esperan que queden en 38C (100F) por varios d\u00edas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mitin de Trump Retrasado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Serena Williams has withdrawn from her planned Wimbledon doubles match with her older sister Venus due to a knee injury.\",            \"english_title\": \"Serena Williams Withdraws\",            \"translated_version\": \"Serena Williams se retir\u00f3 de su partido de dobles planeado en Wimbledon con su hermana mayor Venus debido a una lesi\u00f3n en la rodilla.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Serena Williams se Retira\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pope paid tribute to migrants who died at sea at a cemetery on the Italian island of Lampedusa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pope Honors Migrants\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Papa rindi\u00f3 homenaje a los migrantes que murieron en el mar en un cementerio en la isla italiana de Lampedusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Papa Honra a Migrantes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky says the goal is to target key infrastructure that makes money for Russia's war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Zelensky's Strategy\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania, Volodymyr Zelensky, dice que el objetivo es atacar infraestructura clave que hace dinero para la guerra de Rusia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Estrategia de Zelensky\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"West Bengal's decision to replace eggs in some school meals has started a bigger discussion about nutrition and choice.\",            \"english_title\": \"School Meal Changes\",            \"translated_version\": \"La decisi\u00f3n de Bengala Occidental de reemplazar huevos en algunas comidas escolares ha comenzado una discusi\u00f3n m\u00e1s grande sobre nutrici\u00f3n y elecci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cambios en Comidas Escolares\"        }    ]}"